@item @command{putnextctl1(9)} @tab -- put a 1 byte control message to the next STREAMS queue
@item @command{putnextctl(9)} @tab -- put a control message to the next STREAMS queue
@item @command{qprocsoff(9)} @tab -- disable STREAMS queue procedures
@item @command{qprocson(9)} @tab -- enable STREAMS queue procedures
@item @command{unfreezestr(9)} @tab -- release exclusive access from a STREAMS queue
@item @command{MPSTR_QLOCK(9)} @tab -- lock a STREAMS queue for exclusive access
@item @command{MPSTR_QRELE(9)} @tab -- unlock a STREAMS queue from exclusive access
